OL,3,CFormer Pride in London boss admits
OL,4,Ccontempt of court
OL,6,FThe suspended chief executive of Pride
OL,7,Fin London has admitted contempt of
OL,8,Fcourt after failing to hand back login
OL,9,Fdetails for its social media and bank
OL,10,Faccounts.
OL,12,FEvent organiser London LGBT Community
OL,13,FPride CIC alleged that Christopher
OL,14,FJoell-Deshields had tried to block its
OL,15,Faccess to bank accounts and social
OL,16,Fmedia by taking passwords, login
OL,17,Fdetails and a mobile phone with him
OL,18,Fafter he was suspended over
OL,19,Fallegations of serious misconduct.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
