FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1776957068
OL,3,CFormer Pride in London boss admits
OL,4,Ccontempt of court
OL,6,FLawyers for the organisation have told
OL,7,Fprevious hearings that he had failed
OL,8,Fto return the items despite being
OL,9,Fordered to do so by a High Court judge
OL,10,Fin September.
OL,12,FA hearing was due to be held earlier
OL,13,Fthis week to decide whether this
OL,14,Famounted to contempt.
OL,16,FBut in a court order Mr Justice Cotter
OL,17,Fsaid that Mr Joell-Deshields "admits
OL,18,Fthat he acted in contempt of the
OL,19,Fcourt" by failing to return the items.
OL,26,@yD@^OU{D@FO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
