OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1776957068
OL,3,CFormer Pride in London boss admits
OL,4,Ccontempt of court
OL,6,FThe order said that Mr Joell-Deshields
OL,7,F"failed to deliver up" various
OL,8,Fdocuments, a WeWork pass and a SIM
OL,9,Fcard which belonged to Pride in
OL,10,FLondon, as well as plans for holding
OL,11,Fan event in Vauxhall Pleasure Gardens
OL,12,Fin the capital.
OL,14,FIt also said that he failed to provide
OL,15,Fusernames or passwords for several of
OL,16,FPride in London's online accounts,
OL,17,Fincluding Facebook, HM Revenue and
OL,18,FCustoms, PayPal and YouTube.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@VO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
