FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1776957068
OL,3,CFormer Pride in London boss admits
OL,4,Ccontempt of court
OL,6,FThe order said that Mr Joell-Deshields
OL,7,Fwill be sentenced for the contempt in
OL,8,FJune or July.
OL,10,FHe will also be sentenced for a second
OL,11,Fallegation of contempt for failing to
OL,12,Ffile a witness statement, which he
OL,13,Fadmitted in January.
OL,15,FContempt can result in a sentence of
OL,16,Fup to two years in prison or a fine.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
