PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1776957068
OL,3,CFormer Pride in London boss admits
OL,4,Ccontempt of court
OL,6,FAt a hearing in March, David
OL,7,FCunnington, for Pride in London, said
OL,8,Fthat the organisation took legal
OL,9,Faction against Mr Joell-Deshields as
OL,10,Fit was concerned he wanted to "develop
OL,11,Fa rival organisation" using
OL,12,Fconfidential information obtained in
OL,13,Fhis role as chief executive.
OL,26,@rD@_OUsD@UO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
