PN,40206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1776957068
OL,3,CFormer Pride in London boss admits
OL,4,Ccontempt of court
OL,6,FMr Cunnington said the organisation
OL,7,Fwants to stop Mr Joell-Deshields from
OL,8,Fhaving "any and all confidential
OL,9,Finformation recorded in documentary
OL,10,Fform or stored in any digital or
OL,11,Felectronic form belonging to the
OL,12,Fclaimant or any of its funders,
OL,13,Fsponsors, customers, suppliers or
OL,14,Fagents, comprising technical,
OL,15,Ffinancial and business information".
OL,26,@pD@HOUwD@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
