PN,40207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1776957068
OL,3,CFormer Pride in London boss admits
OL,4,Ccontempt of court
OL,6,FDeputy High Court Judge Matthew Butt
OL,7,FKC ordered that the court would find
OL,8,Fin Pride in London's favour in the
OL,9,Fclaim if Mr Joell-Deshields did not
OL,10,Ffile a defence by April 13, which was
OL,11,Fnot done.
OL,13,FDamages in the claim are to be
OL,14,Fdetermined at a later date, with Mr
OL,15,FJoell-Deshields blocked from using,
OL,16,Fpublishing, holding or deleting
OL,17,Fcompany property or its confidential
OL,18,Finformation.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
